animals

Class Animal

  • java.lang.Object
    • animals.Animal
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ape, Bear, Elephant, Giraffe, Lion, Penguin, Tiger

    public abstract class Animal
extends java.lang.Object
    Animal class will be the basis for all different animal classes. Class defines the basic properties and methods that all the different animal classes will use. it will allow them to eat, excrete and grow old
